<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="confusion-n">confusion <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /kən'fjuːʒən/    美 /kən'fjuːʒən/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-u">1.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 混乱；杂乱：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>fall into confusion
陷入混乱</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>mental confusion
精神错乱</p></div>

<h4 id="2-u">2.★ <strong>[U] 混淆；弄错：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>To avoid confusion, the teams wore different colours.
为避免混淆，各队都穿了不同颜色的服装。</p></div></div>